description:
Basket, straw, American Indian (Pima), XXc NO SPECIFIC PHOTO AND DIMS. ON CAT. CARD (GROUP INFORMATION)
Basket with pinched handle and double mouth; fine coilwork.  Design consists of stepped radial rectangles, possibly a modified whirlwind pattern.  Colors are natural and black.
title: Basket
